What's My Name: Muhammad Ali

"What's My Name Muhammad Ali" is a documentary film that delves into the life and legacy of legendary boxer Muhammad Ali. Through archival footage, interviews, and personal recordings, the film showcases Ali's boxing career, his activism, and his enduring impact as one of the most iconic figures in sports history.
